《'''百事可樂：足球音樂季'''》（{{Lang-en|'''Pepsi Beats of the Beautiful Game'''}}）是一張群星合輯，於2014年6月12日開始的[[2014年世界盃足球賽|2014年世界杯足球賽]]之前的2014年6月9日發行<ref name="Explore">{{cite web|url=http://www.pepsi.com/en-us/d/content/3340/Explore-Pepsi-Beats-of-the-Beautiful-Game|title=Explore Pepsi Beats of the Beautiful Game|work=[[Pepsi|Pepsi]]|accessdate=May 9, 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141028161225/http://www.pepsi.com/en-us/d/content/3340/Explore-Pepsi-Beats-of-the-Beautiful-Game|archivedate=2014年10月28日|df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6084764/pepsi-beats-beautiful-game-world-cup-album-kelly-rowland-timbaland|title="Beats of the Beautiful Game," curated by Pepsi, will be released June 10 ahead of the World Cup|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|accessdate=May 12, 2014|archive-date=2020-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925210221/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6084764/pepsi-beats-beautiful-game-world-cup-album-kelly-rowland-timbaland|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
[[百事可樂|百事可樂]]極度（Pepsi Max）最先將各首歌曲作為單曲於數位媒體網路商店[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]]發售，而各首歌曲的音樂錄影帶亦可於影片分享網站[[YouTube|YouTube]]和[[Vevo|Vevo]]免費觀看<ref name="pepsi.com"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/brazil-world-cup-rita-ora-3530628|title=Kelly Rowland and Rita Ora set for World Cup album ahead of Brazil 2014|work=mirror.co.uk|accessdate=May 12, 2014|archive-date=2019-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190601091721/https://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/brazil-world-cup-rita-ora-3530628|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

